@doc overview
@name gaiafrontend.css.Buttons
@description
<p>Use any of the available button classes to quickly create a styled button.</p>
<h1 class="h2">Style Classes</h1>
<h2 class="h3">Default</h2>
<p>The default GAIA app button.</p>
<div class="well">
    <p>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default">Default</button>
        <button type="button" disabled="disabled" class="btn btn-default">Disabled</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default active">Pushed</button>
    </p>
    <h3 class="h4">Jade</h3>
    <pre>
      button.btn.btn-default(type="button") Default
      button.btn.btn-default(type="button", disabled="disabled") Disabled
      button.btn.btn-default.active(type="button") Pushed            
  </pre>
</div>
<h2 class="h3">Primary</h2>
<p>The outstanding button, for the more important actions.</p>
<div class="well">
    <p>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Primary</button>
        <button type="button" disabled="disabled" class="btn btn-primary">Disabled</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary active">Pushed</button>
    </p>
    <h3 class="h4">Jade</h3>
    <pre>
    button.btn.btn-primary(type="button") Primary
    button.btn.btn-primary(type="button", disabled="disabled") Disabled
    button.btn.btn-primary.active(type="button") Pushed
</pre>
</div>
<h2 class="h3">Navigation</h2>
<p>Used only for navigation actions inside .btn-navigation-group</p>
<div class="well">
    <p>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-navigation">Navigation</button>
        <button type="button" disabled="disabled" class="btn btn-navigation">Disabled</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-navigation active">Pushed</button>
    </p>
    <h3 class="h4">Jade</h3>
    <pre>
    button.btn.btn-navigation(type="button") Navigation
    button.btn.btn-navigation(type="button", disabled="disabled") Disabled
    button.btn.btn-navigation.active(type="button") Pushed
    </pre>
</div>
<h2 class="h3">Icons inside Buttons</h2>
<p>Icons in buttons are added by classes. This type or class are estructured as follows:</p>
<div class="well">
    <p>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-after-paste">Paste</button>
    </p>
    <h3 class="h4">Jade</h3>
    <pre>
    button.btn.btn-default<span class="nt">.btn-icon-after-paste</span>(type="button") Paste
    </pre>
</div>
<p>This class name
    <kbd>.btn-icon-after-paste</kbd>indicates the type of icon and where is located.</p>
<p>The word after indicates the icon is located after the content of the button, here we can use
    <kbd>before</kbd>or
    <kbd>after</kbd>.</p>
<p>The word paste, indicates the icon.</p>
<h4>Icon Examples</h4>
<div class="well">
    <h2 class="h3">Arrow Buttons</h2>
    <p>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-before-prev">Previous</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-after-next">Next</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-icon-before-prev">Prevous</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-icon-after-next">Next</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-navigation btn-icon-before-prev">Previous</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-navigation btn-icon-after-next">Next</button>
    </p>
    <h3 class="h4">Jade</h3>
    <pre>
    button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-before-prev(type="button") Previous
    button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-after-next(type="button") Next
    button.btn.btn-primary.btn-icon-before-prev(type="button") Prevous
    button.btn.btn-primary.btn-icon-after-next(type="button") Next
    button.btn.btn-navigation.btn-icon-before-prev(type="button") Previous
    button.btn.btn-navigation.btn-icon-after-next(type="button") Next
    </pre>
</div>
<div class="well">
    <h2 class="h3">Icons Buttons (Before Icon Examples)</h2>
    <p>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-before-cancel">Cancel</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-before-checked">Checked</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-before-copy">Copy</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-before-detail">Detail</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-before-edit">Edit</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-before-exit">Exit</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-before-maximize">Maximize</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-before-new">New</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-before-paste">Paste</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-before-save">Save</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-before-user">User</button>
    </p>
    <h3 class="h4">Jade</h3>
    <pre>
    button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-before-cancel(type="button") Cancel
    button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-before-checked(type="button") Checked
    button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-before-copy(type="button") Copy
    button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-before-detail(type="button") Detail
    button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-before-edit(type="button") Edit
    button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-before-exit(type="button") Exit
    button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-before-maximize(type="button") Maximize
    button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-before-new(type="button") New
    button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-before-paste(type="button") Paste
    button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-before-save(type="button") Save
    button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-before-user(type="button") User
    </pre>
</div>
<div class="well">
    <h2 class="h3">Icons Buttons (After Icon Examples)</h2>
    <p>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-after-cancel">Cancel</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-after-checked">Checked</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-after-copy">Copy</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-after-detail">Detail</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-after-edit">Edit</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-after-exit">Exit</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-after-maximize">Maximize</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-after-new">New</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-after-paste">Paste</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-after-save">Save</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-after-user">User</button>
    </p>
    <h3 class="h4">Jade</h3>
    <pre>
      button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-after-cancel(type="button") Cancel
      button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-after-checked(type="button") Checked
      button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-after-copy(type="button") Copy
      button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-after-detail(type="button") Detail
      button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-after-edit(type="button") Edit
      button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-after-exit(type="button") Exit
      button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-after-maximize(type="button") Maximize
      button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-after-new(type="button") New
      button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-after-paste(type="button") Paste
      button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-after-save(type="button") Save
      button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-after-user(type="button") User
    </pre>
</div>
<h1 class="h2">Button Groups</h1>
<h2 class="h3">Btn Group Form</h2>
<p>Used in the bottom of forms, to align right buttons</p>
<div class="well">
    <p>
        <div class="btn-group-form">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-icon-after-cancel">Cancel</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Agree</button>
        </div>
    </p>
    <h3 class="h4">Jade</h3>
    <pre>
    .btn-group-form
        button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-after-cancel(type="button") Cancel
        button.btn.btn-primary(type="button") Agree
    </pre>
</div>
<h2 class="h3">Btn Group Navigation</h2>
<p>Used to fix the navigation bar in the bottom of the app, and add navigation buttons.</p>
<div class="well">
    <p>
        <div style="position:relative" class="btn-group-navigation">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-navigation pull-left">Previous</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-navigation">Next</button>
        </div>
    </p>
    <h3 class="h4">Jade</h3>
    <pre>
    .btn-group-form
        button.btn.btn-default.btn-icon-after-cancel(type="button") Cancel
        button.btn.btn-primary(type="button") Agree
    </pre>
</div>
